# app-ads-proxy (DMZ) — runtime config for the upload-only fence in front of MinIO.
# Copy to proxy.env on the DMZ VM and fill in. The proxy holds ZERO credentials
# (DESIGN.md §3 inv 2). Injected at container start by docker-entrypoint.sh.

# The form origin allowed to upload (CORS). Must be the exact scheme+host of the form.
ALLOW_ORIGIN=https://ads.gpsaswimming.org
